I would like to have an overview of how many of my agents are being used during peak hours.
- max/min no. of agents used during a day/week/month;
- total amount (minutes, hours) of builds waiting in a queue;

We need this in order to proper estimate how many build agents we need (as the license is linked to no. of agents).

